Tuan Muda Klao, jangan!

703
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:29,980
Err, tumpang tanya. Ini penggambaran drama ke?

704
00:48:30,340 --> 00:48:34,120
Err, saya tak berniat nak ganggu, tapi...

705
00:48:35,560 --> 00:48:40,640
Boleh sesiapa beritahu saya di mana pintu keluar studio?

706
00:48:45,820 --> 00:48:48,980
Klao lari ke mana?

707
00:48:53,320 --> 00:48:54,340
Klao.

708
00:48:56,440 --> 00:48:59,560
Baguslah dah balik. Mari makan sekali.

709
00:49:02,840 --> 00:49:04,460
Tak... tak apalah.

710
00:49:05,800 --> 00:49:06,860
Prayong.

711
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:08,900
Ya, tuan.

712
00:49:10,120 --> 00:49:11,900
Klao sudah gila ke?

713
00:49:15,340 --> 00:49:19,920
Ya Tuhan, kasihan sungguh budak ini.

714
00:49:23,640 --> 00:49:25,420
Klao, Klao.

715
00:49:26,700 --> 00:49:27,360
Klao.

716
00:49:28,100 --> 00:49:31,230
-Mari sini kita bercakap.
-Aduh, jangan ikut saya lagi.

717
00:49:37,460 --> 00:49:39,360
Aduh, ya Tuhan. Jatuh tangga.

718
00:49:39,380 --> 00:49:40,260
Maafkan saya.

719
00:49:40,460 --> 00:49:43,200
Aduh, hampir saya jatuh tangga sekali.

720
00:49:58,380 --> 00:50:00,780
Kalau bukan kru penggambaran, saya ada di mana sebenarnya?

721
00:50:00,780 --> 00:50:03,780
Merentas masa ke zaman lampau, mustahil.

722
00:50:04,400 --> 00:50:06,440
Lagi satu, siapa lelaki tadi itu?

723
00:50:06,920 --> 00:50:08,050
Tak dapat ingatlah.

724
00:50:08,260 --> 00:50:09,920
Tapi cara dia pandang saya,

725
00:50:09,940 --> 00:50:11,940
macam sudah lama kenal.

726
00:50:13,920 --> 00:50:16,940
Tuan Klao, Tuan Klao.

727
00:50:17,820 --> 00:50:19,980
Tuan Klao, jangan lari lagi.

728
00:50:33,540 --> 00:50:34,620
Tuan Klao.

729
00:50:35,620 --> 00:50:38,860
Pegang kuat-kuat. Jangan bergerak, Tuan Klao.

730
00:50:39,460 --> 00:50:41,120
Tuan Klao, jangan bergerak.

731
00:50:41,980 --> 00:50:44,440
Tuan Klao, patik sudah kata jangan meronta.

732
00:50:44,960 --> 00:50:46,600
Jangan meronta.

733
00:50:48,240 --> 00:50:49,020
Aduh!

734
00:50:55,060 --> 00:50:57,390
Kan saya sudah kata jangan ikut saya lagi.

735
00:50:57,720 --> 00:51:00,240
Tolong! Sesiapa tolong saya! Aduh!

736
00:51:00,740 --> 00:51:01,660
Klao.

737
00:51:02,480 --> 00:51:04,820
Sesiapa pun boleh, asalkan bukan dia.

738
00:51:06,700 --> 00:51:08,100
Mari sini kita bercakap.

739
00:51:08,760 --> 00:51:10,100
Tak nak.

740
00:51:10,400 --> 00:51:13,260
Aduh, Tuan Klao. Awak tak apa-apa?

741
00:51:20,600 --> 00:51:21,780
Huh, ke tepi.

742
00:51:23,840 --> 00:51:25,970
Saya boleh layan awak sepanjang hari.

743
00:51:29,230 --> 00:51:30,500
Dang, dang, dang, dang.

744
00:51:30,500 --> 00:51:32,960
Aduh, kalah juga dengan suara dalam kepala.

745
00:51:36,060 --> 00:51:40,190
Semua orang berlakon dengan bagus. Latar tempat pun nampak sangat nyata.

746
00:51:40,440 --> 00:51:42,520
Ini mungkin bukan kru penggambaran.

747
00:51:47,320 --> 00:51:48,780
Alamak.

748
00:51:49,320 --> 00:51:50,920
Tuan Klao, awak kenapa?

749
00:51:54,880 --> 00:51:57,200
Sakitnya, tapi tak boleh bangun.

750
00:51:57,700 --> 00:51:59,520
Ini bukan mimpi.

751
00:52:03,520 --> 00:52:05,780
Sindiket penipuan takkan buat sampai macam ini.

752
00:52:05,780 --> 00:52:07,400
Jadi saya sudah merentas ke mana ini?

753
00:52:07,400 --> 00:52:08,530
Kampung terpencil?

754
00:52:08,780 --> 00:52:10,840
Atau ajaran sesat macam dalam filem?

755
00:52:16,380 --> 00:52:18,160
Tuan Klao, Tuan Klao.

756
00:52:18,700 --> 00:52:19,820
Tuan Klao, berhentilah.

757
00:52:19,820 --> 00:52:20,440
Tuan Klao.

758
00:52:21,280 --> 00:52:21,840
Ayam.

759
00:52:21,840 --> 00:52:23,570
Patik sudah tak larat nak lari.

760
00:52:24,660 --> 00:52:25,440
Tuan Klao.

761
00:52:26,820 --> 00:52:28,350
Tuan Klao, awak nak ke mana?

762
00:52:32,720 --> 00:52:34,150
Tuan Klao, cukuplah.

763
00:52:34,410 --> 00:52:36,670
-Tuan Klao!
-Saya akan lawan balik, hoi!

764
00:52:39,560 --> 00:52:41,420
Tuan Klao, bertenang.

765
00:52:42,080 --> 00:52:43,270
Tuan Klao, hati-hati.

766
00:52:43,270 --> 00:52:44,470
Tuan Klao, cukuplah.

767
00:52:48,420 --> 00:52:49,620
Cukuplah, Tuan Klao.

768
00:52:54,100 --> 00:52:55,920
Aduh, apa benda ini?

769
00:52:56,600 --> 00:52:58,020
Jangan ke sana.

770
00:52:59,260 --> 00:53:00,680
Tuan Klao.

771
00:53:00,680 --> 00:53:01,370
Tolong!

772
00:53:01,700 --> 00:53:02,440
Tuan Klao.

773
00:53:15,200 --> 00:53:16,480
Berhenti, berhenti.

774
00:53:21,260 --> 00:53:24,720
Jangan datang dekat, atau saya akan sumpah kalian.

775
00:53:24,860 --> 00:53:25,880
Saya akan sumpah setiap seorang daripada kalian.

776
00:53:25,880 --> 00:53:27,140
Nak buat macam mana ya?

777
00:53:27,140 --> 00:53:28,900
Espresso dengan buih susu.

778
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:31,160
Wah, sedapnya buih susu itu.

779
00:53:51,320 --> 00:53:53,660
Betul ke saya sudah merentas ke zaman purba?

780
00:53:53,660 --> 00:53:55,720
Macam mana saya boleh sampai ke sini?

781
00:53:56,320 --> 00:53:59,140
Biasanya kalau sebut tentang merentas masa,

782
00:54:02,340 --> 00:54:05,230
kita akan terfikir tentang mesin masa,

783
00:54:05,470 --> 00:54:08,100
sihir, atau sejenis ilmu magis,

784
00:54:08,920 --> 00:54:11,500
ataupun pintu gerbang masa.

785
00:54:11,780 --> 00:54:18,080
Kadang-kadang watak utama pengsan,

786
00:54:18,800 --> 00:54:20,800
atau terlibat dalam kemalangan,

787
00:54:20,900 --> 00:54:23,830
yang menyebabkan dia merentas kembali ke masa lalu.

788
00:54:24,080 --> 00:54:29,820
Kembali ke masa lalu biasanya dianggap bermula dengan kematian.

789
00:54:30,320 --> 00:54:32,450
Maksudnya, mati dalam kehidupan ini.

790
00:54:32,560 --> 00:54:36,800
Dan dilahirkan semula dalam jasad yang baharu di kehidupan lain.

791
00:54:38,340 --> 00:54:42,340
Pintu masa. Ah, macam main permainan video.

792
00:54:42,480 --> 00:54:45,160
Kalau mati di peringkat ini, boleh hidup semula dan mula sekali lagi.

793
00:54:45,160 --> 00:54:48,160
Mungkin saya mabuk teruk sampai boleh berada di sini.

794
00:54:48,640 --> 00:54:52,300
Kalau saya mati sekarang, saya boleh kembali ke zaman moden, kan?

795
00:54:53,340 --> 00:54:56,340
Tuan Phop, sudah lama turun ke bawah.

796
00:54:57,880 --> 00:54:59,360
Perlukah kami...

797
00:56:01,820 --> 00:56:01,820
Sila ikut sini, tuan tabib.

798
00:56:01,820 --> 00:56:06,100
[Pratonton Episod Seterusnya]

799
00:56:06,100 --> 00:56:07,140
Thee.

800
00:56:07,340 --> 00:56:08,140
Abang Klao.

801
00:56:08,500 --> 00:56:10,400
Pun, baguslah. Saya dah selamat.

802
00:56:10,520 --> 00:56:13,540
Abang Klao betul-betul dah gila macam yang Abang Jom cakap.

803
00:56:13,540 --> 00:56:15,620
Awak ni, kalau fasal Klao,

804
00:56:15,680 --> 00:56:17,720
awak nampak lebih risau daripada hal awak sendiri.

805
00:56:17,720 --> 00:56:20,280
Tuan Phop yang muka ketat itu, dia dah ada isteri ke?

806
00:56:20,280 --> 00:56:24,080
Tak pernah nampak Tuan Phop ambil berat atau pedulikan sesiapa pun.

807
00:56:24,480 --> 00:56:27,120
Pada pandangan hamba, orang yang dia ambil berat,

808
00:56:27,120 --> 00:56:29,000
hanyalah Tuan Muda Klao.

809
00:56:34,950 --> 00:56:35,600
